{"tid":1024029,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"叔叔「北」行了","createTime":"2019-02-16T08:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T16:44:42.000Z","uid":166821,"like":6,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2642cea34b5ce1020be1af4d6aea21ce9e09b046","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"一年了。<br />\n<br />\n依然是一個人、一個背囊、一張機票。<br />\n<br />\n可能，再加上一個自圓其說的理由。<br />\n<br />\n又一次，踏出自己的comfort zone，去征服地圖上另一個標記。<br />\n<br />\n北韓。<br />\n<br />\n雖然近幾年北韓旅遊團流行於市，北韓的面貌不再神秘。<br />\n<br />\n但我都想來這個神秘國度打打卡，告訴自己，曾經在南北韓統一前，留下過腳毛，在這個鐵幕國度遊走過。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊的意義，每個人都不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n最近幾次旅行都令我對旅遊的熱度退減，感覺吃喝玩樂的行程已經不能滿足自己。<br />\n<br />\n在台灣街道上閒逛，與其他文青一樣，走進了書局，在暢銷書排行榜上隨手摘下一本書，便感覺自己品味提升了。<br />\n<br />\n書名叫《何苦去旅行》<br />\n<br />\n只看到序言，便觸動到內心。<br />\n<br />\n資訊發達無疑拉近了世界的距離，呢個世代去旅行只要動動手指，一部手機，機票、火車飛、酒店、民宿，什麼評價評論排山倒海地湧出來，未出發，先感沒趣。<br />\n<br />\n就好似一套俾人劇透過無數次的電影，一點新鮮感、一點值得期待的感覺都沒有。<br />\n<br />\n地圖上一個又一個地方被開發、攻佔、瞬間變旅遊熱點。<br />\n<br />\n北韓，不外如是。<br />\n<br />\n「逃出羊角島其實係行程之一。」<br />\n<br />\n「住西山酒店啦，幾年前裝修完，比起羊角島更新淨，仲平三舊水。」<br />\n<br />\n網上搜尋「北韓」或「朝鮮」等字眼，不難找到相關詳細的賽後感。<br />\n<br />\n今次旅程，行程相信同一般遊記差不多。<br />\n<br />\n搭飛機北上北京，然後轉火車一路向北，經瀋陽，往中國最靠近的邊境城市，丹東。<br />\n<br />\n就在這裡作為旅程的起點。<br />\n<br />\n叔叔對世界的枯燥感到不行了，急不及待要玩玩了。<br />\n<br />\n最後，願我出走一排，歸來仍舊完好無缺，阿門。"},{"pid":"66f00cd5311cf0dd134ed992b19b9b3b0204c171","tid":1024029,"uid":9942,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T16:01:03.000Z","msg":"上年去過 其實好安全 唔使打咁大篇文仲要加標點符號。"},{"pid":"11ce7e02a4124f08f531274d7a2e5971ebee633c","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:21:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.imgur.com/gallery/nMsgJo3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.imgur.com%2Fgallery%2FnMsgJo3&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L9lAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=1de3ecab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.imgur.com/gallery/nMsgJo3</a><br />\n<br />\n到北京。"},{"pid":"d41e5667ac928936f2020d4b4a33047927f2c2d7","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMJk55j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMJk55j.png&h=39645685&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df0568a77da7c4ae9d847316ffa7057ee8a6240a","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVPXoSk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVPXoSk.png&h=0ff63a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右邊為 蝕緊錢的海航crew。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arHqxLH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarHqxLH.png&h=cddabb4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搭緊機鐵出市區。"},{"pid":"cd7b2983b905268b4f2d9acb7c5a45d06931f7a2","tid":1024029,"uid":1330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:32:15.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"fe30f645b5baa502d83b5de49e79a15f306e4c79","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOwZCek.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOwZCek.png&h=81c89221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係呢個柒菇碌包包<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90379d07fba4f16403cab851ba60b6c558d96deb","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pmjAaDd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpmjAaDd.png&h=b7ca64e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家轉車去故宮附近食 北京烤鴨，<br />\n然後下午應該成日行程就係行故宮。"},{"pid":"cc38d658db771352ed08b9e3497a24122f0ecaad","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TURCpLb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTURCpLb.png&h=c1ea1512&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QHxX5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QHxX5e.png&h=8bcbc276&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/17/140719_e3711b1485ec9f6da9c972181dc21ff1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F17%2F140719_e3711b1485ec9f6da9c972181dc21ff1.png&h=d4f28ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/17/140728_19aa4a56532456e832d036f4c116172e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F17%2F140728_19aa4a56532456e832d036f4c116172e.png&h=23eabd24&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/17/140751_237942742259c285064f6b2adc8aaf4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F17%2F140751_237942742259c285064f6b2adc8aaf4d.png&h=ff2bdbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家故宮轉左網上買飛，明明昨晚上網睇都仲有400幾張，而家一票難求。<br />\n<br />\n來到北京，遇正星期日，終於明白咩叫做蝗禍。<br />\n<br />\n諗住去食北京都算出名既烤鴨連鎖店，四季民福烤鴨，點知要等150張檯。<br />\n<br />\n諗住攞飛，有個大媽過左張檯，係度同個知客理論。<br />\n<br />\n發現大陸d服務業真係對d西客太上心啦，下下動真氣，完全無理會後面百幾人等緊你攞籌。<br />\n<br />\n無錯，我啊。<br />\n<br />\n頭先搭地鐵又係。<br />\n<br />\n出閘個陣去客戶服務中心度補飛<br />\n<br />\n有個大姐係度話佢張飛出唔到閘，平時都出到。<br />\n<br />\n大媽話一直都唔可以出。<br />\n<br />\n大姐就話一直都出到，用左兩年都得。<br />\n<br />\n大媽就話一直都唔得。<br />\n<br />\n大姐就話一直係幾耐。<br />\n<br />\n大媽就話，一直就係而家呢一刻直到宇宙毀滅。<br />\n<br />\n大姐又問，宇宙毀滅之後呢。<br />\n<br />\n大媽冷笑話，呢個世界就係因為有你呢d人阻住地球轉。<br />\n<br />\n點解我會咁清楚d對話。<br />\n<br />\n因為我睇左兩次周星馳套《新喜劇之王》<br />\n<br />\n同埋，我就係個個排佢後面被逼聽左成10分鐘呢d無營養既對話。<br />\n<br />\n講返轉頭，個知客講講下激動到自己另轉面係度飲泣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬啊，你專業得唔得啊。<br />\n<br />\n我要張籌姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住隔離個大媽係度安慰佢。<br />\n<br />\n仲唔係機會，飛雲。<br />\n<br />\n我即刻係褲袋拎左張皺既紙巾俾佢。<br />\n<br />\n好似搞到我地兩個整喊佢咁，係度tum小朋友咁。<br />\n<br />\n霞姨！<br />\n<br />\n搵個專業d既知客得唔得啊，成村人等緊佢派籌啊。<br />\n<br />\n廚房個肥佬終於睇唔順眼，出來幫手派飛。<br />\n<br />\n一位。<br />\n<br />\n佢望一望我。<br />\n<br />\n我一睇。<br />\n<br />\n屌！<br />\n<br />\n你前面還有155張檯在等候。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbabba0de11dcb1ca9b1f56607a2f31f0f42ee88","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoGSd2E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoGSd2E.png&h=6ad18413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個人午餐"},{"pid":"7ab54954c2551eb8c449d6e18633166f8837722c","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"小二，上菜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eaA35bA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeaA35bA.png&h=f00eaaf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0edX9Di.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0edX9Di.png&h=a13cba40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60mfbRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60mfbRG.png&h=d83c193f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23baaef3a19e09678faf828c29a2b5a5f06a0181","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:35:28.000Z","msg":"諗起神探入面林雪<br />\n<br />\n紅燒翅，蒸條斑，半隻炸子雞，加碗白飯。<br />\n<br />\n就好想食野。"},{"pid":"3beaf04a20b8eebcfb30c344d9c4a2ee7632ee98","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T19:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/18/030644_38c94b258c0ee89d2dd450e9f5e0622e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F18%2F030644_38c94b258c0ee89d2dd450e9f5e0622e.png&h=53509dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於到瀋陽，出發去丹東。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0hx2qg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0hx2qg.png&h=331e1f05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"377662012d518268bf5a13398c2487aa66307cad","tid":1024029,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T21:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1412977c192547e2ccbc152c30d185adc89e9378","tid":1024029,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T22:28:19.000Z","msg":"咁刷得"},{"pid":"6d8c2120edd62491c8218ef4f9d718f39d417869","tid":1024029,"uid":166821,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7Vzyca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7Vzyca.png&h=cc9a6155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓簽證，出發啦。"},{"pid":"e0127ba8641e23a2a7a380920e6a9381f82325e7","tid":1024029,"uid":36483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"原來live緊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85e36ddabe65089afefca5118f6963b5cc3a4d1","tid":1024029,"uid":36483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"樓主俾金仔溶左?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}